Class AttributeTypeImpl

java.lang.Object
  EObjectImpl

All Implemented Interfaces:
AttributeType
public class AttributeTypeImpl
extends EObjectImpl
implements AttributeType

An implementation of the model object 'Attribute Type'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Description
  • Display Name
  • Icon
  • Attribute Name
  • Attribute Class
  • Default Value
  • Suggested Value
  • Attribute Extension
  • Id
